description:
This diagram depicts the human peripheral blood mononuclear cell (PBMC) immune signaling network. PBMCs are a critical component of the immune system, helping fight infection and adapt to intruders. The diagram is modified from Figure S6 of Bodenmiller et al., 2012.

References
- Bodenmiller, B. et al. (2012) Multiplexed mass cytometry profiling of cellular states perturbed by small-molecule regulators. Nat. Biotechnol., 30, 858-867.
author: Jonathan Karr
